title: North West Is a Total Cutie in Mom Kim Kardashian's Latest Snapchats
text:
BY: Brandi Fowler 
Can North West get any more adorable?! 
Kim Kardashian West and Kanye West 's 3-year-old daughter—who is a total Snapchat pro—had yet more fun with her mom on the social networking site, with the duo Snapping away together as they enjoyed their family vacation in Costa Rica. 
In several Snaps the Keeping Up with the Kardashian star shared Monday, little Northie and Kim transformed into everything from barking pups to raccoons, and they couldn't resist the ubiquitous glowing floral crown. A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 30, 2017 at 1:23pm PST A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 30, 2017 at 2:26pm PST 
"Are you so beautiful?" Kim asked her daughter as they munched on cookies, with North smiling at the camera in a denim Jacket. "Yeah," she replied. They even sang together as Kim put a bunny filter on North (who is looking more and more like her mom). It's almost too much cuteness for one day. A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 30, 2017 at 1:28pm PST A video posted by Kim Kardashian Snapchats (@kimksnapchats) on Jan 30, 2017 at 1:40pm PST 
The mother-daughter duo has been living it up with the rest of the Kardashian-Jenner clan during their winter getaway. Sunday night, Kim left her little ones at home, though, as she stepped out for dinner with Kylie Jenner and the rest of the fam. 
Kim showed off her curves in a sheer metallic Paco Rabanne dress paired with a navy suede baseball cap and lace-up sandals, and Jenner stunned in a plunging fringe white dress.
